<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Confidance</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #fafafa;
      color: #333;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .hero {
      background: #2c3e50;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 80px 20px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 48px;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .hero p {
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }

    h2 {
      color: #2c3e50;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    .card {
      background: white;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 15px 0;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #777;
    }

    a {
      color: #2c3e50;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <div class="hero">
    <h1>Confidance</h1>
    <p>Move. Connect. Feel confident.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="container">

    <div class="card">
      Confidance is a space for people to connect through music, movement, fitness, and friendship. 
      We create a welcoming environment where everyone can feel comfortable, supported, and empowered.
    </div>

    <h2>What We Offer</h2>

    <div class="card">Yoga Classes – strength, flexibility, calm</div>
    <div class="card">Barre Classes – tone, posture, control</div>
    <div class="card">Dance Classes – expression, rhythm, fun</div>
    <div class="card">Corporate Yoga – wellness for teams</div>
    <div class="card">Workshops & Events – special experiences</div>

    <h2>Our Mission</h2>

    <div class="card">
      To help you feel stronger, more confident, and more connected—physically and mentally.
    </div>

    <h2>Contact</h2>

    <div class="card">
      Email: <a href="mailto:your@email.com">your@email.com</a>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    © Confidance
  </div>

</body>
</html>
